text.tspan: My work experience includes full-stack web
development and mobile app design.
I created front-end UIs, back-end apps and websites using HTML,
CSS, JS, Angular, React, WPF, Node.Js, Ruby Rails, MongoDB and
PostGreSql. Some examples are a loan service for automating
processing applications, global hybrid cloud disaster recovery
system, a multi-tenant PaaS/ SaaS networking tool and SEO tools.
I follow an agile design philosophy using sprint based planning
and execution, following industry standards and applying object oriented design
and analysis for developing websites. My apps work cross-platform on Windows,
MacOs/ IOS and Linux/ Unix environments.
I create original artwork for my websites including wireframes, web layouts,
templates, icons and scenes for animation. I bring the scenes to life by
meticulously animating effects. The end result is a beautiful, pixel-perfect
transition that adds a lively flair to the content in bringing creative ideas to life.
I volunteer for non-profit
organizations and consultant
for end-clients.
I completed the Web
Development Immersive
course at General Assembly.
My end-clients include Ellie Mae,
Leidos Health, Philips Healcare Analytics,
Microsoft, Cisco, and Blue Shield, CA.
My skills are full-stack web
development, QA, Data Science
and Machine Learning.
